First Department,

December, 1936.

(December 1, 1936.)) Joseph Russo, and Others, Appellants, v. Title Guarantee and Trust Company, Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements, and case placed on calendar for trial on December 7, 1936. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., McAvoy, Townley, Glennon and Cohn, JJ.
